S.FORM: Etdrick Bohannon nalecuhan i San Bernardino, California, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. 5 bulad 29 demiad, 1973 a mihca, Etdrick Bohannon, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
